{"tid":964323,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【公告】曼聯球迷放假指定動作！！！","createTime":"2019-01-01T08:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T06:04:28.000Z","uid":141519,"like":124,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8147bbc1281d174b58c65bcecd4cb8ae7fdf3eb4","tid":964323,"uid":141519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:44:22.000Z","msg":"朝早起身: J 連迪路夫紋身圖 <br />\r\n早餐食紅雞蛋，一條心，撐紅魔！ <br />\r\n睇番98/99三冠王珍藏版dvd，拎定三卷tempo廁紙，以防睇到歐聯反勝階段走火 <br />\r\n<br />\r\nlunch搭水晶觀光巴士食lunch<br />\r\n慶祝今季脫離大巴足球，食一餐贏一場，聯賽38連勝指日可待 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n下午剪新髮型扮普巴，練琴扮山齊士，開電腦J碧咸/費格遜/蘇斯克查/雲佩斯<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJ完換曼聯(作客)波衫落街，買架雪佛蘭(曼聯sponsor)，揸到扯扯地。 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n晚飯係全日重點，著住全套曼聯波衫波褲，手持Manchester United F.C 頸巾，去尖沙咀Manchester United Restaurant Bar，大唱會歌共20202020次，20字=20次英超聯聯冠軍。 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n晚上安然跳上曼聯床單睡床，準備夢見全隊曼聯職球員夢遺！"},{"pid":"ded74abede9e2c65eb5d4cdf9b6e9a0cdd3fd844","tid":964323,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a39af0d34c846a8821674548ee316c64b8752a8","tid":964323,"uid":141519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ded74abede9e2c65eb5d4cdf9b6e9a0cdd3fd844","tid":964323,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17058119ca3d1cdc36be08fe5c5caaa25b1a7bd","tid":964323,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"計劃了照做了得到了 時間卻太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hk